[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/roman_key_card"]
[Student "S"]
{With eleven cards in the "round" suits EAST has a lot of playing strength. So when WEST bids 
a Limit Raise in \Hs EAST wants to know about Aces.

RKCBlackwood tells him that WEST has two Aces plus the trump Queen, so EAST can see that 6\H 
is practically a certainty.}

